  "text": "Polyethylene is one of the five main plastics produced today [CITATION_1] . To determine if T. gratilla larvae ingested microspheres, and if so, whether there were any effects on larval survival and growth, the larvae were exposed to fluorescent green polyethylene microspheres at four concentrations; 1, 10, 100 and 300 spheres.mL -1 (in FSW for the duration of the study [CITATION_2] .",
